---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions | MoveCostMatrix" description="Terms and conditions for using MoveCostMatrix. Free moving cost calculator for planning purposes only." canonical="/terms">
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://movecostmatrix.com/" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Terms and Conditions", "item": "https://movecostmatrix.com/terms" }
      ]
    }
  </script>
  <Nav currentPath="/terms" />

  <main>
  <section class="bg-canvas px-4 pb-28 pt-16 sm:pb-36 sm:pt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-mute">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-mute">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-body content">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By using MoveCostMatrix (the &ldquo;Service&rdquo;), you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Service Description</h2>
        <p>MoveCostMatrix provides a free, browser-based moving cost calculator. The estimates generated are for <strong>planning purposes only</strong> and are not guaranteed quotes from any moving company. Actual costs may vary based on factors including but not limited to: weight of belongings, fuel surcharges, labor rates, seasonal demand, stair-carries, and packing materials.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">No Guarantee of Accuracy</h2>
        <p>We strive to make our distance and cost calculations as accurate as possible using the Haversine formula, public postal-code APIs, and industry-average per-mile rates. However, we make no warranty, express or implied, regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any estimate. You should obtain binding quotes from licensed moving companies before making financial decisions.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>The information provided by MoveCostMatrix does not constitute professional moving, financial, or legal advice. Always consult qualified professionals for advice specific to your situation.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>The Service may contain links to third-party websites, including moving companies and service providers. We do not endorse, control, or assume responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>MoveCostMatrix, the MoveCostMatrix logo, and all original content on this site are the property of MoveCostMatrix. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>MoveCostMatrix and its operators shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Service. Use the Service at your own risk.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these terms, <a href="/contact" class="text-link underline">contact us here</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  </main>

  <Footer currentPath="/terms" />
</Layout>
